description:

<p>
Designing and implementing a multi-brand accessible design system unified the brand identities and expanded the user base while ensuring consistency and efficiency across platforms. The new system streamlined collaboration across product, marketing, and engineering teams, reduced design redundancies by <strong>55%</strong>, and accelerated feature rollouts by <strong>30%</strong>, improving customer satisfaction and saving budgets.
</p>
